00:05:05.910 --> 00:05:07.980 align:middle line:84%
If all goes well,
condemnations can

00:05:07.980 --> 00:05:10.950 align:middle line:84%
lead to sanctions which
increases social misery

00:05:10.950 --> 00:05:12.840 align:middle line:90%
and only helps your cause.

00:05:12.840 --> 00:05:14.610 align:middle line:84%
And that, my friends,
is how you can

00:05:14.610 --> 00:05:16.960 align:middle line:90%
destabilize an entire society.

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:20.110 align:middle line:84%
What we will see today are
several examples of this way

00:05:20.110 --> 00:05:22.150 align:middle line:90%
