00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:52.980 align:middle line:84%
As the crisis worsened and
anti-British feeling mounted,

00:06:52.980 --> 00:06:55.980 align:middle line:84%
Iranian army units were
deployed to maintain order.

00:06:55.980 --> 00:07:01.275 align:middle line:90%


00:07:01.275 --> 00:07:04.460 align:middle line:84%
As the Iranian authorities
moved to take over oil plants

00:07:04.460 --> 00:07:07.480 align:middle line:84%
and docks and the British
technicians unanimously

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:10.365 align:middle line:84%
refused to accept employment
with the new regime,

00:07:10.365 --> 00:07:11.985 align:middle line:90%
