00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:18.220 align:middle line:90%
With the US and UK, not so much.

00:07:18.220 --> 00:07:20.440 align:middle line:10%
This kicked off a
regime change operation

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:23.890 align:middle line:10%
greenlit by Winston Churchill
in the UK and Dwight Eisenhower

00:07:23.890 --> 00:07:28.000 align:middle line:10%
in the US, run by the
CIA and known as Ajax.

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:32.380 align:middle line:84%
It resulted in a coup against
the Iranian government in 1953.

00:07:32.380 --> 00:07:35.020 align:middle line:84%
The CIA official in charge
of orchestrating events

00:07:35.020 --> 00:07:38.380 align:middle line:84%
was Kermit Roosevelt, grandson
of former President Teddy

00:07:38.380 --> 00:07:39.940 align:middle line:90%
Roosevelt.

00:07:39.940 --> 00:07:42.680 align:middle line:84%
Operation Ajax involved
several things.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:45.010 align:middle line:84%
One was detonating
a series of bombs

00:07:45.010 --> 00:07:48.640 align:middle line:84%
by the agents posing as
members of the Communist Party.

00:07:48.640 --> 00:07:50.680 align:middle line:84%
These were actually
Iranian agents

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:53.110 align:middle line:84%
working for US and
British intelligence.

00:07:53.110 --> 00:07:54.970 align:middle line:84%
In other words,
kill innocent people

00:07:54.970 --> 00:07:57.130 align:middle line:84%
by planting explosives
and then blaming

00:07:57.130 --> 00:08:00.070 align:middle line:84%
the communists and also
groups loyal to the Mosaddegh

00:08:00.070 --> 00:08:01.550 align:middle line:90%
government.

00:08:01.550 --> 00:08:05.530 align:middle line:84%
Now, we know the CIA was behind
this since they've admitted it.

00:08:05.530 --> 00:08:08.320 align:middle line:84%
What we don't know is
the extent of this tactic

00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:10.780 align:middle line:84%
since the CIA
destroyed nearly all

00:08:10.780 --> 00:08:13.210 align:middle line:84%
of its files
relating to the coup.

00:08:13.210 --> 00:08:16.660 align:middle line:84%
We do know that at least one
well-known Muslim's house

00:08:16.660 --> 00:08:20.072 align:middle line:84%
