posing as communists.

00:08:20.072 --> 00:08:21.280 align:middle line:90%
That much has been confirmed.

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:24.580 align:middle line:84%
And we also know that some
of the most feared gangsters

00:08:24.580 --> 00:08:30.130 align:middle line:84%
in Tehran were hired by the
CIA to stage pro-Shah riots

00:08:30.130 --> 00:08:31.810 align:middle line:90%
