00:08:42.370 --> 00:08:44.530 align:middle line:84%
Another tactic was
bribing demonstrators

00:08:44.530 --> 00:08:46.810 align:middle line:84%
into chanting
pro-Mosaddegh slogans

00:08:46.810 --> 00:08:48.820 align:middle line:84%
while violently
attacking symbols

00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:51.910 align:middle line:84%
of the Shah, who was
essentially the king of Iran

00:08:51.910 --> 00:08:53.920 align:middle line:90%
and supported by the US.

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:55.840 align:middle line:84%
And this would be
like paying people

00:08:55.840 --> 00:08:58.270 align:middle line:84%
