in order to discredit

00:08:58.270 --> 00:09:00.220 align:middle line:90%
an organization or movement.

00:09:00.220 --> 00:09:03.190 align:middle line:10%
In this case, the point
was to turn public opinion

00:09:03.190 --> 00:09:05.920 align:middle line:10%
