and for the Shah.

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:07.240 align:middle line:90%
It worked.

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:09.490 align:middle line:84%
Quite a few very
unsavory characters

00:09:09.490 --> 00:09:11.320 align:middle line:90%
