00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:45.940 align:middle line:84%
That's equivalent to
$657 million today.

00:09:45.940 --> 00:09:48.940 align:middle line:84%
Another key person in the
coup was Bahram Shahrohk,

00:09:48.940 --> 00:09:51.670 align:middle line:84%
